description:
Dan says it is looking difficult for the Big 10 to get a fall football season in this year. Dan names the teams that will not be playing and says that will leave the Big 10 with not enough teams to play. Dan says now Big 10 players are pushing back to playing in the spring and Dan believes that spring football will not be happening.
